00:01:06.320 --> 00:01:08.670
Prince Zhenbei's Mansion won't
let this go easily.

00:01:09.000 --> 00:01:11.800
Ran, don't be afraid. I'm here with you.

00:01:12.280 --> 00:01:15.590
I have only you in my heart.

00:01:16.030 --> 00:01:19.110
If I marry someone, it will only be you.

00:01:20.110 --> 00:01:21.360
