00:02:34.000 --> 00:02:35.030
Listen carefully.

00:02:35.030 --> 00:02:36.400
Those poisoned by this poison

00:02:36.480 --> 00:02:39.630
will lose their inner strength
and suffer unbearable pain.

00:02:39.880 --> 00:02:41.400
Killing you now

00:02:41.710 --> 00:02:44.150
is easier than killing an ant.

00:02:44.440 --> 00:02:45.400
Today,

00:02:45.840 --> 00:02:48.400
I'll personally send you on your way.

00:02:52.070 --> 00:02:53.150
Farewell.

00:03:15.510 --> 00:03:16.670
Why?

00:03:17.030 --> 00:03:18.760
Because you killed Zhijin.

00:03:19.800 --> 00:03:21.630
